title: Fabrice Metz
text:
Fabrice Metz (born 23 January 1991 in <a href="Strasbourg">Strasbourg</a>, <a href="France">France</a>) is a French professional <a href="rugby%20union">rugby union</a> player. He plays at <a href="lock%20%28rugby%20union%29">lock</a> for <a href="Section%20Paloise">Section Paloise</a> in the <a href="Top%2014">Top 14</a>.
Fabrice Metz has also played for the following teams: <a href="Oyonnax%20Rugby">Oyonnax</a>, Pau, France (national).
